      "start": 632.3,
      "end": 633.68,
      "text": "He's a little hesitant"
    },
    {
      "start": 633.68,
      "end": 636.46,
      "text": "I think he's on his granddaughter's side"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.46,
      "end": 638.1,
      "text": "but he doesn't want to say it"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.1,
      "end": 639.0,
      "text": "Not yet"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.0,
      "end": 641.9,
      "text": "아직 속내를 밝히시진 않았지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.9,
      "end": 645.64,
      "text": "왠지 손녀딸과 같은 배를 타지 않을까"
    },
    {
      "start": 645.64,
      "end": 646.66,
      "text": "예상을 하면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 646.66,
      "end": 648.16,
      "text": "다시 들어볼게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 648.16,
      "end": 649.88,
      "text": "Did you read it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 650.46,
      "end": 651.86,
      "text": "It's your dad's company now"
    },
    {
      "start": 651.86,
      "end": 653.42,
      "text": "It was yours once"
    },
    {
      "start": 653.42,
      "end": 654.98,
      "text": "Yours and mom's"
    },
    {
      "start": 654.98,
      "end": 656.52,
      "text": "In no time at all"
    },
    {
      "start": 656.52,
      "end": 657.68,
      "text": "You'll be sitting on the board"
    },
    {
      "start": 657.68,
      "end": 658.66,
      "text": "with your quarter share"
    },
    {
      "start": 658.66,
      "end": 659.94,
      "text": "and you can debate your dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 659.94,
      "end": 660.74,
      "text": "as much as you want"
    },
    {
      "start": 660.74,
      "end": 661.88,
      "text": "It'll be too late by then"
    },
    {
      "start": 661.88,
      "end": 662.88,
      "text": "They'll have dug up"
    },
    {
      "start": 662.88,
      "end": 663.92,
      "text": "half of Western Australia"
    },
    {
      "start": 663.92,
      "end": 666.28,
      "text": "I'm just a link to all clients"
    },
    {
      "start": 666.28,
      "end": 667.68,
      "text": "I don't make policy anymore"
    },
    {
      "start": 667.68,
      "end": 670.94,
      "text": "네, 방지연님께서요"
    },
    {
      "start": 670.94,
      "end": 672.38,
      "text": "크크크크쌤"
    },
    {
      "start": 672.38,
      "end": 673.76,
      "text": "오늘도 반가워요"
    },
    {
      "start": 673.76,
      "end": 676.28,
      "text": "즐겁게 공부할 수 있게 해주셔서 감사해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 676.28,
      "end": 677.32,
      "text": "Oh, no problem"
    },
    {
      "start": 677.32,
      "end": 678.32,
      "text": "Thank you"
    },
    {
      "start": 678.32,
      "end": 680.24,
      "text": "유쾌하게 인사를 해주셨습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 680.24,
      "end": 682.52,
      "text": "와, 오늘도 수고하셨고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 682.52,
      "end": 683.66,
      "text": "아, 네, 조쌤도"
    },
    {
      "start": 683.66,
      "end": 684.92,
      "text": "네, 그럼 우리는"
    },
    {
      "start": 684.92,
      "end": 686.24,
      "text": "See you next Monday"
    }
  ]
}